  "topic": "Fortnite",
  "summary": "Fortnite is an online video game where players are dropped onto an island and must battle against each other to be the last one standing. Aspects of the game such as V-Bucks currency, building defenses, and power-ups can be used to understand various arithmetic concepts. With its rich lore and continual updates, it provides several contexts for constructing interesting word problems. Fortnite is an online video game where players compete against each other to be the last one standing. It is rich in contextual mathematical topics including V-Bucks currency, building defenses and various power-ups to understand different arithmetic concepts. P...",
